## What Good Looks Like
Short. Specific. One clear ask. Sounds like a person, not a pitch deck.

Bad: "I wanted to reach out and share how IBM Planning Analytics can leverage AI to drive synergies in your FP&A process..."

Good: "Noticed [Company] is still running scenarios manually in [Anaplan]. Finance teams in [industry] I work with are getting the same output in a fraction of the time with AI handling the model updates. Worth 10 minutes to see what that looks like?"
